exactly at the right time.

01:59:56.672 --> 02:00:01.310 line:90% position:50% align:center
And what an abundance
of spiritual food we have!

02:00:01.310 --> 02:00:04.814 line:90% position:50% align:center
Just think of the variety that we discussed

02:00:04.814 --> 02:00:06.949 line:90% position:50% align:center
in our annual meeting today

02:00:06.949 --> 02:00:10.519 line:90% position:50% align:center
