02:00:20.796 --> 02:00:24.300 line:90% position:50% align:center
<i>The Good News According to Jesus</i>
video project,

02:00:24.300 --> 02:00:28.504 line:90% position:50% align:center
as well as the wonderful,
upbuilding spiritual songs.

02:00:28.504 --> 02:00:31.240 line:90% position:50% align:center
And that’s just a fraction

02:00:31.240 --> 02:00:34.410 line:90% position:50% align:center
