02:01:03.839 --> 02:01:06.042 line:90% position:50% align:center
How vital it is, brothers,

02:01:06.042 --> 02:01:08.611 line:90% position:50% align:center
that we continue to recognize

02:01:08.611 --> 02:01:12.381 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah’s channel
for receiving spiritual food!

02:01:13.215 --> 02:01:18.220 line:90% position:50% align:center
The November 15, 2013,
issue of <i>The Watchtower</i>

02:01:19.121 --> 02:01:23.726 line:90% position:50% align:center
mentioned key points
for elders in particular to keep in mind

02:01:23.726 --> 02:01:26.929 line:90% position:50% align:center
as we prepare to face the attack

02:01:26.929 --> 02:01:29.465 line:90% position:50% align:center
of that coalition of nations

02:01:29.465 --> 02:01:33.703 line:90% position:50% align:center
that the Bible calls Gog of Magog.

02:01:33.703 --> 02:01:36.205 line:90% position:50% align:center
Now I’m going to quote the article;
this is what it stated.

02:01:36.205 --> 02:01:39.809 line:90% position:50% align:center
This is the quote: “At that time,

02:01:39.809 --> 02:01:44.547 line:90% position:50% align:center
“life-saving direction
that we receive from Jehovah’s organization

02:01:44.547 --> 02:01:48.884 line:90% position:50% align:center
“may not appear practical
from a human standpoint.

02:01:50.086 --> 02:01:53.189 line:90% position:50% align:center
“All of us must be ready to obey

02:01:53.189 --> 02:01:55.891 line:90% position:50% align:center
“any instructions we may receive,

02:01:55.891 --> 02:01:57.893 line:90% position:50% align:center
“whether these appear sound

02:01:57.893 --> 02:02:02.798 line:90% position:50% align:center
“from a strategic or human standpoint
or not. . . .

02:02:03.733 --> 02:02:05.735 line:90% position:50% align:center
“Now is the time

02:02:05.735 --> 02:02:10.539 line:90% position:50% align:center
“for any who may be putting
their trust in secular education,

02:02:10.539 --> 02:02:12.708 line:90% position:50% align:center
“material things,

02:02:12.708 --> 02:02:15.411 line:90% position:50% align:center
“or human institutions

02:02:15.411 --> 02:02:18.114 line:90% position:50% align:center
to adjust their thinking.”

02:02:19.281 --> 02:02:21.617 line:90% position:50% align:center
Very sober words

02:02:21.617 --> 02:02:25.321 line:90% position:50% align:center
that apply so well at this particular moment.

02:02:26.422 --> 02:02:30.559 line:90% position:50% align:center
So, dear brothers and sisters,
do you know what time it is?

02:02:30.559 --> 02:02:33.429 line:90% position:50% align:center
There has never been
a more important time

02:02:33.429 --> 02:02:36.432 line:90% position:50% align:center
to stay alert spiritually

02:02:36.432 --> 02:02:39.335 line:90% position:50% align:center
and to respond quickly

02:02:39.335 --> 02:02:41.437 line:90% position:50% align:center
to Jehovah’s direction.

02:02:41.437 --> 02:02:45.174 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah has led us safely to this moment.

02:02:45.174 --> 02:02:48.677 line:90% position:50% align:center
He has given us everything that we need,

02:02:48.677 --> 02:02:51.480 line:90% position:50% align:center
and we know he’s going to continue to do so

02:02:51.480 --> 02:02:54.450 line:90% position:50% align:center
—just as our 2022 yeartext

02:02:54.450 --> 02:02:57.920 line:90% position:50% align:center
found at Psalm 34:10 states:

02:02:57.920 --> 02:03:02.925 line:90% position:50% align:center
“Those seeking Jehovah
will lack nothing good.”

02:03:03.626 --> 02:03:05.694 line:90% position:50% align:center
So, dear brothers and sisters,

02:03:05.694 --> 02:03:07.763 line:90% position:50% align:center
be determined

02:03:07.763 --> 02:03:12.134 line:90% position:50% align:center
to continue to follow
our Leader, Jesus Christ,

02:03:12.134 --> 02:03:15.004 line:90% position:50% align:center
and the channel that he is using today

02:03:15.004 --> 02:03:17.273 line:90% position:50% align:center
because if we do,

02:03:17.273 --> 02:03:20.543 line:90% position:50% align:center
we will have everything that we need

02:03:20.543 --> 02:03:23.379 line:90% position:50% align:center
and right on time.

02:03:29.919 --> 02:03:33.122 line:90% position:50% align:center
Well, with that we conclude
another spiritual feast

02:03:33.122 --> 02:03:35.124 line:90% position:50% align:center
in conjunction with the annual meeting

02:03:35.124 --> 02:03:38.127 line:90% position:50% align:center
of the Watch Tower Bible
and Tract Society of Pennsylvania.

02:03:39.261 --> 02:03:42.531 line:90% position:50% align:center
Wasn’t that a powerful program?

02:03:42.531 --> 02:03:46.102 line:90% position:50% align:center
And how reassuring
to review the many ways

02:03:46.102 --> 02:03:49.805 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah has strengthened us,
energized us,

02:03:49.805 --> 02:03:52.908 line:90% position:50% align:center
and comforted us over the last year!

02:03:52.908 --> 02:03:56.312 line:90% position:50% align:center
This annual meeting
left us with no doubt

02:03:56.312 --> 02:03:58.314 line:90% position:50% align:center
that despite the challenges

02:03:58.314 --> 02:04:00.583 line:90% position:50% align:center
our brothers and sisters have had to endure

02:04:00.583 --> 02:04:02.685 line:90% position:50% align:center
in the face of persecution,

02:04:02.685 --> 02:04:04.820 line:90% position:50% align:center
natural disasters,

02:04:04.820 --> 02:04:08.023 line:90% position:50% align:center
and the ongoing effects of the pandemic,

02:04:08.023 --> 02:04:12.027 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah continues to bless his people.

02:04:12.027 --> 02:04:16.699 line:90% position:50% align:center
His organization is on the move
as never before.

02:04:17.600 --> 02:04:21.137 line:90% position:50% align:center
Let’s conclude our program
with a video postcard

02:04:21.137 --> 02:04:26.142 line:90% position:50% align:center
that takes us
to the beautiful island nation of Jamaica.

02:04:26.142 --> 02:04:30.813 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jamaica is the third-largest island
in the Caribbean Sea,

02:04:30.813 --> 02:04:33.349 line:90% position:50% align:center
located about 100 miles,

02:04:33.349 --> 02:04:35.417 line:90% position:50% align:center
or 160 kilometers,

02:04:35.417 --> 02:04:37.419 line:90% position:50% align:center
west of Haiti.

02:04:37.419 --> 02:04:39.021 line:90% position:50% align:center
The golden beaches

02:04:39.021 --> 02:04:42.291 line:90% position:50% align:center
and beautiful coral reefs
that ring the island

02:04:42.291 --> 02:04:46.262 line:90% position:50% align:center
draw more than four million visitors
each year.

02:04:46.262 --> 02:04:49.965 line:90% position:50% align:center
The country’s main crops include bananas,

02:04:49.965 --> 02:04:51.567 line:90% position:50% align:center
sugarcane,

02:04:51.567 --> 02:04:55.404 line:90% position:50% align:center
and world-famous
Jamaican blue mountain coffee,

02:04:55.404 --> 02:04:59.875 line:90% position:50% align:center
which is grown high
on the steep slopes of the Blue Mountains.

02:04:59.875 --> 02:05:03.579 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jamaica is also known for its jerk cuisine,

02:05:03.579 --> 02:05:07.983 line:90% position:50% align:center
which features meats
such as chicken, pork, or goat

02:05:07.983 --> 02:05:11.687 line:90% position:50% align:center
rubbed with spices and cooked over a fire

02:05:11.687 --> 02:05:15.558 line:90% position:50% align:center
to give the meat a distinctive smoky flavor.

02:05:15.558 --> 02:05:20.563 line:90% position:50% align:center
The good news first reached Jamaica in 1897.

02:05:20.563 --> 02:05:22.998 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brother Russell even gave a talk

02:05:22.998 --> 02:05:27.403 line:90% position:50% align:center
in the capital city of Kingston back in 1913.

02:05:28.170 --> 02:05:33.175 line:90% position:50% align:center
Today, there are
more than 11,360 publishers

02:05:33.175 --> 02:05:37.646 line:90% position:50% align:center
preaching in more than 165 congregations

02:05:37.646 --> 02:05:39.515 line:90% position:50% align:center
and groups.

02:05:39.515 --> 02:05:42.551 line:90% position:50% align:center
The national language of Jamaica is English,

02:05:43.552 --> 02:05:45.821 line:90% position:50% align:center
but two remote translation offices

02:05:45.821 --> 02:05:48.791 line:90% position:50% align:center
help support the preaching in Jamaican Creole

02:05:48.791 --> 02:05:51.527 line:90% position:50% align:center
and Jamaican Sign Language.

02:05:51.527 --> 02:05:53.529 line:90% position:50% align:center
During the pandemic

02:05:53.529 --> 02:05:55.998 line:90% position:50% align:center
when it became necessary
to hold meetings

02:05:55.998 --> 02:05:58.000 line:90% position:50% align:center
by videoconference,

02:05:58.000 --> 02:06:02.238 line:90% position:50% align:center
our Jamaican brothers
had to deal with a special challenge

02:06:02.238 --> 02:06:06.408 line:90% position:50% align:center
—the high price of Internet access.

02:06:06.408 --> 02:06:09.878 line:90% position:50% align:center
The cost of data
to connect to just one meeting

02:06:09.878 --> 02:06:14.049 line:90% position:50% align:center
was twice the price
of taking a taxi to the Kingdom Hall.

02:06:14.049 --> 02:06:18.487 line:90% position:50% align:center
So it was far more expensive
to attend a meeting virtually

02:06:18.487 --> 02:06:20.489 line:90% position:50% align:center
than it was to attend in person.

02:06:20.489 --> 02:06:22.925 line:90% position:50% align:center
Our Jamaican brothers and sisters

02:06:22.925 --> 02:06:26.295 line:90% position:50% align:center
generously have been sharing
their electronic devices

02:06:26.295 --> 02:06:29.798 line:90% position:50% align:center
and helping one another
with the cost of data

02:06:29.798 --> 02:06:33.302 line:90% position:50% align:center
so that everyone can access the meetings

02:06:33.302 --> 02:06:35.971 line:90% position:50% align:center
and enjoy good association.

02:06:35.971 --> 02:06:38.574 line:90% position:50% align:center
Some who benefited from these provisions

02:06:38.574 --> 02:06:42.511 line:90% position:50% align:center
are in the Central Sign Language Congregation
in Mandeville.

02:06:43.212 --> 02:06:47.216 line:90% position:50% align:center
The congregation has been able
to meet together by videoconferencing

02:06:47.216 --> 02:06:50.619 line:90% position:50% align:center
with two other
Jamaican Sign Language groups,

02:06:50.619 --> 02:06:52.621 line:90% position:50% align:center
providing deaf publishers on the island

02:06:52.621 --> 02:06:55.724 line:90% position:50% align:center
with more opportunities for association

02:06:55.724 --> 02:06:57.726 line:90% position:50% align:center
during the pandemic.

02:06:58.894 --> 02:07:00.229 line:90% position:50% align:center
The hardworking publishers

02:07:00.229 --> 02:07:02.698 line:90% position:50% align:center
in the Central Sign Language Congregation

02:07:02.698 --> 02:07:05.534 line:90% position:50% align:center
send you their love and greetings.

02:07:06.235 --> 02:07:09.471 line:90% position:50% align:center
And please remember,
dear brothers and sisters,

02:07:09.471 --> 02:07:12.608 line:90% position:50% align:center
that we love you all very much.

